 *    6. Graph edges must have a "minlen" property.
 *
 * Post-conditions:
 *
 *    - Graph nodes will have their rank adjusted to ensure that all edges are
 *      tight.
 *
 * Returns a tree (undirected graph) that is constructed using only "tight"
 * edges.
 */
